   <SYNC START=4330935>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4331135>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- Reinforce the rear and left flanks.<br>- Yes, sir.
   <SYNC START=4333645>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4333847>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- no one fires unless i give the order.<br>- "(cadets)" yes, sir.
   <SYNC START=4338357>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4397169>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Too much! There must be<br>100 trucks coming in here.
   <SYNC START=4400839>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4401090>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Don't sweat it.
   <SYNC START=4403280>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4422739>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>"(woman over loudspeaker) stephen miller? "
   <SYNC START=4424929>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4426577>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>"stephen miller? "
   <SYNC START=4428967>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4429163>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>"it's mom, honey. "
   <SYNC START=4431153>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4432292>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>"will you listen to me, please? "
   <SYNC START=4434802>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4437214>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>"it's still not too late to come out of there"<br>"and forget it ever happened. "
   <SYNC START=4442654>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4442971>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>"we have such a wonderful summer"<br>"planned for you. "
   <SYNC START=4446721>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
