   <SYNC START=5236891>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5237165>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Maybe I underestimated those damn tapes.
   <SYNC START=5239885>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5240085>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Kids I can understand,<br>Hulk was always marginal, but West.
   <SYNC START=5243475>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5243714>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>It was a big mistake, Brian,<br>if you don't mind me saying.
