      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>He'd tell us to hold out.
   <SYNC START=5258148>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5258355>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah, I know he would.
   <SYNC START=5261105>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5263236>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Why don't you go grab some sleep? Go on.
