   <SYNC START=5268160>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5268325>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Me? Slept like a baby this afternoon.<br>Two whole hours.
   <SYNC START=5272235>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5272496>
