   <SYNC START=5331921>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5332106>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Hey! I don't wanna hear anyone<br>bad-mouth West.
   <SYNC START=5335656>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5335902>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>He did what he felt was right.
   <SYNC START=5338572>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5340240>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- Put guards on the water supplies.<br>- Yes, sir.
   <SYNC START=5343150>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5343369>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Brian!
   <SYNC START=5345089>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5355632>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>"mash! "
   <SYNC START=5357142>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5357301>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>"(indistinct conversation)"
   <SYNC START=5359811>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5368647>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Any news?
   <SYNC START=5370837>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5374320>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You want the news? I'll give you the news.
   <SYNC START=5377520>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5377741>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>We take you now to reporter Alex Dwyer<br>on the scene of the uprising.
   <SYNC START=5381941>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5382788>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I'm outside the gates of Bunker Hill Academy<br>talking to a National Guardsman,
   <SYNC START=5386458>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5386709>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>a young man not much older than the infants<br>who have taken over this old institution.
   <SYNC START=5391379>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5391673>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Let's see what the grunt on the street says.
   <SYNC START=5394063>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5394260>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Trooper, how do you feel about the<br>possibility of taking this school by force?
   <SYNC START=5398460>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5398723>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- Give me those!<br>- I'd like to frag the freaks!
   <SYNC START=5400953>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5401143>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Sir, what's your opinion of this crisis?
   <SYNC START=5403453>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5403645>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I feel sorry for the little cherubs. It's<br>society's fault. We failed to meet the needs...
   <SYNC START=5407765>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5408025>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Thank you, Private Bleeding Heart.
   <SYNC START=5409695>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5409861>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>We take you now to a press meeting,<br>live in progress,
   <SYNC START=5412741>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5412948>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>with Colonel Adolf Kerby<br>of the National Guard.
   <SYNC START=5416148>
