   <SYNC START=5418358>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5418537>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>It's the governor's fervent hope that force<br>will not be necessary in retaking the school.
   <SYNC START=5423927>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5424252>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>However, the governor will not stand by<br>indefinitely and allow this to continue.
   <SYNC START=5428962>
