   <SYNC START=5542923>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5543179>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- They turned off the power.<br>- Turn 'em on!
   <SYNC START=5545329>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5545515>
