   <SYNC START=5891546>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5891825>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I wanna stay alive in situations where it ain't<br>easy, but you, my friend, you're a death lover.
   <SYNC START=5897735>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5898082>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I know the species.
   <SYNC START=5900432>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5900627>
