   <SYNC START=5904177>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5904423>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Somebody sold you on the idea<br>that dying for a cause is romantic.
   <SYNC START=5907773>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5908010>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Well, that is the worst kind<br>of all the kinds of bullshit there is!
   <SYNC START=5912050>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5912307>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Dying is only one thing. Bad.
   <SYNC START=5916187>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5917396>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Don't find that out. Please.
